{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f6634c1b00","title":"井冈山红卫兵筹备建立委员会第一号决议──关于组织原则","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2f84fd9484","index":0,"year":1966,"month":9,"day":23,"articleId":"f6634c1b00"}],"tags":[{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"550a5d8a4b","name":"清华大学井冈山红卫兵筹备建立委员会"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7319c066d7","type":"title","text":"井冈山红卫兵筹备建立委员会第一号决议──关于组织原则","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"},{"id":"981786dfdd","type":"authors","text":"清华大学井冈山红卫兵筹备建立委员会","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"},{"id":"1d10e802b5","type":"paragraph","text":"我们井冈山红卫兵坚决贯彻党的阶级路线。井冈山红卫兵是以红五类为主体的革命的组织。第一，有成份论；第二，不唯成份论；第三，重在政治表现。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"},{"id":"97a8b00e06","type":"paragraph","text":"什么样的人可以加入我们的组织？","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"},{"id":"87c5d03736","type":"paragraph","text":"基本条件：","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"},{"id":"3adcc837ef","type":"paragraph","text":"一、 他们是“敢”字当头，富有彻底的革命造反精神。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"},{"id":"fabc5fc2eb","type":"paragraph","text":"二、 他们必须要坚决地，全面地，不折不扣地贯彻十六条，努力学习毛泽东思想，照毛主席指示办事。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"},{"id":"a66f37f90a","type":"paragraph","text":"三、 他们必须用接班人五条标准时时刻刻要求自己。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"},{"id":"49eeec39b9","type":"paragraph","text":"四、 他们必须要向解放军学习，坚决贯彻三八作风。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"},{"id":"c30a2d6055","type":"paragraph","text":"五、 他们必须甘当群众小学生，善于听取群众意见。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"},{"id":"795e4588f8","type":"paragraph","text":"六、 他们必须富有自我批评精神，知错就改。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"},{"id":"51ed555dab","type":"paragraph","text":"七、 他们必须是红五类子弟和一般出身的同志。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"},{"id":"8a141f4c2c","type":"paragraph","text":"现在他们的基本观点必须是：","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"},{"id":"34beccd1a5","type":"paragraph","text":"一、 认为临筹执行的是错误路线，并且敢造其反。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"},{"id":"f62613af8b","type":"paragraph","text":"二、 认为毛泽东思想红卫兵总部犯了右倾错误。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"},{"id":"a1c47b4e67","type":"paragraph","text":"同意上述观点的非红五类子弟可加入井冈山战斗团。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"},{"id":"a507ce7225","type":"paragraph","text":"报名处：到二宿舍212领表填写。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"},{"id":"7591708236","type":"paragraph","text":" 井冈山红卫兵筹备建立委员会召集人：蒯大富、彭伟民、鲍长康一九六六年九月二十三日","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00"}],"page":{"id":"6d6c4670da","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f6634c1b00","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}